    Package Description
    Localization
    The Localization package contains the classes related to the localization-related classes.
    Navigation
    package contains navigation-related classes (Navigation, Odometer, OdometryCorrection, Avoidance) that work together to allow the vehicle to roam around the playing field and react to the sensor data.
    Utilities
    Package contains every utilities used for many purposes to simplify the software architecture and eliminate method repetition among classes.
